OCD Delian League: "The Egyptian expedition ended in disaster for Athens in 454, and in that year the treasury was moved from Delos to Athens (?for security in this moment of peril; but the date of the move is not absolutely certain)."

Plutarch mentions the treasury move in *Life of Pericles* section 12.

Egyptian Expedition- Thucydides 1.110

Diodorus 11.85- Sosistratus was archon "Athenians controlled a great number of cities"

Diodorus  11.38- 8,000 talents transferred from Delos to Athens